name: SkyPix
0:
”Alexa, start Sky Pix”
”Alexa, open Sky Pix”
”Alexa, ask Sky Pix for help”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: sky pix
des:
On Echo devices with screen this skill shows random pictures from the NASA service "Astronomy picture of the day" (APOD). 

If interested the image description texts are read for you. But you may skip instead and proceed with the next picture.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
